Changes for the CPAN Testers Blog website
=========================================

1.13    2015-12-31
        - added CSS green ribbon promotion.

1.12    2015-10-11
        - updates from live
        - upgrade to Labyrinth-Plugin-CPAN-3.55.
        - added CPAN Testers Sponsor adverts.
        - added 1 <3 CPAN Testers framed ribbon.

1.11    2015-09-15
        - upgrade to Labyrinth-5.32.
        - upgrade to Labyrinth-Plugin-Core-5.19.

1.10    2015-02-09
        - upgrade to Labyrinth-5.24.
        - removed Perl promotions links.
        - added Admin site links.

1.09    2014-09-21
        - fixed license fields in META.json to be lists.
        - added documentation about the CPAN Testers Fund.

1.08    2014-05-23
        - upgrade to Labyrinth-5.21.
        - upgrade to Labyrinth-Plugin-Core-5.15.
        - upgrade to Labyrinth-Plugin-Articles-Diary 1.05.
        - upgrade to Labyrinth-Plugin-Event 1.04.
        - fixed distribution name in META.
        - added LICENSE file.
        - added nofollow link attributes to iheart.js.
        - upgraded comment management.
        - extend allowable CMS HTML tags.

1.07    2014-02-16
        - removed unused files.
        - template cleanups.
        - upgrade to Labyrinth-5.20.
        - upgrade to Labyrinth-Plugin-Core-5.14.
        - updated sumhits script.

1.06    2013-03-24
        - optimised static images.
        - minimised CSS.
        - added robots.txt.
        - change to JSON for iheart 
        - split posted by and on onto 2 different lines
        - upgrade to Labyrinth 5.15.
        - added block.grango.org to Block/Allow IPs

1.05    2013-01-06
        - change file dates changed to meet W3CDTF standards.
        - added iheart styles.

1.04    2012-04-22
        - fixed META.json test.

1.03    2012-04-22
        - fixed publish status when saving edited comments.
        - upgrade to Labyrinth 5.12.
        - removed social media bar due to dubious practices.
        - added CPAN Testers Sponsors.
        - added README.
        - added minimum perl version (5.006).
        - fixed test pre-requisites.
        - reworked Makefile.PL for clarity.

1.02    2011-08-18
        - upgrade to Labyrinth 5.09.
        - upgrade to Labyrinth-Plugin-Core 5.09.
        - added titlemaps and pathmaps to settings.ini.
        - WAI WCAG v2.0 compliance updates.
        - update layout to include an update notification.
        - added a new social media bar
        - fixed images and css incorrectly pasted from wiki distro
        - revised banner logo image by Jon 'JJ' Allen.

1.01    2011-06-20
        - updates to improve presentation.
        - included a Terms & Conidtions page to meet EU Cookie Directive.
        - updates to diary and user templates for images.
        - updates to templates for usability compliance.
        - fixes for Posted lookups.
        - upgrade to Labyrinth 5.08.
        - upgrade to Labyrinth-Plugin-Core 5.08.

1.00    2011-04-20
        - upgrade to Labyrinth 5.04.
        - upgrade to Labyrinth-Plugin-Core 5.06.
        - upgrade to Labyrinth-Plugin-Articles-Diary 1.00.
        - upgrade to Labyrinth-Plugin-Event 1.00.
        - packaged for CPAN release.

0.06    2010-11-20
        - user lists now hide special users (Guest), restrict access to users
          of the same or higher access, and prevent priveledged users from
          being deleted.
        - user acls fixed to correctly list folders and access.
        - folder list driven by database, added FolderName function.
        - update to admin templates to make them consistent across sites.

0.05    2010-09-29
        - repositioned site boxes to avoid text and logo clashing.

0.04    2010-09-16
        - added links to Metabase and Labyrinth.
        - upgraded to Labyrinth v5.00.

0.03    2010-01-14
        - added quote.html
        - added Analysis to site family lists.

0.02    2009-07-04
        - added TinyMCE support to comments for public users.
        - fixed bug in saving comments for admin users.

0.01    2009-05-17
        - First released version, based on Labyrinth v4.16
